OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784306880
OL,3,CParents in Wales face the highest
OL,4,Csummer childcare costs, research shows
OL,6,FParents in Wales face the highest
OL,7,Fsummer childcare costs in Britain, new
OL,8,Fresearch shows.
OL,10,FA survey by Coram Family and Childcare
OL,11,Frevealed Wales has seen the steepest
OL,12,Fannual increase in childcare costs,
OL,13,Fwith prices rising by 10% in the last
OL,14,Fyear to #224 per week.
OL,16,FThe findings come at a time where the
OL,17,Fschool holiday season is fast
OL,18,Fapproaching, where parents in Wales
OL,19,Fcould now face an average childcare
OL,20,Fbill of #1,342 over the six-week
OL,21,Fsummer break.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
