CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784306880
OL,3,CParents in Wales face the highest
OL,4,Csummer childcare costs, research shows
OL,6,FThe survey also found that only 5% of
OL,7,Flocal authorities in Wales report
OL,8,Fhaving sufficient holiday childcare
OL,9,Ffor children and young people with
OL,10,Fadditional learning needs.
OL,12,FLydia Hodges, Head of Coram Family and
OL,13,FChildcare, said: "Holiday childcare is
OL,14,Fnow the missing piece of the puzzle.
OL,16,F"All nations have some level of free
OL,17,Fchildcare for pre-school children but
OL,18,Fthe need for childcare doesn't stop
OL,19,Fwhen children reach school age, or
OL,20,Fwhen the school gates close for the
OL,21,Fsummer.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784306880
OL,3,CParents in Wales face the highest
OL,4,Csummer childcare costs, research shows
OL,6,F"In fact, it only increases. Holiday
OL,7,Fchildcare is essential for parents to
OL,8,Ftake and stay in work but, for too
OL,9,Fmany families, the six-week break
OL,10,Fbrings a sharp increase in childcare
OL,11,Fcosts.
OL,13,F"If we are to ease the annual summer
OL,14,Fstress for families, there must be an
OL,15,Facknowledgement that childcare is a
OL,16,Fyear-round requirement."
OL,18,FThe Welsh Government says accessible
OL,19,Fchildcare is key to help children to
OL,20,Fthrive while supporting parents to
OL,21,Fwork.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
