OL,3,CParents in Wales face the highest
OL,4,Csummer childcare costs, research shows
OL,6,FIn a statement it added: "We are
OL,7,Fmaking excellent progress to expand
OL,8,Funiversal funded childcare during the
OL,9,Fearly years, which we know has a huge
OL,10,Fimpact on family income and supports
OL,11,Fchildren's early development.
OL,13,F"We are also supporting local
OL,14,Fauthorities to address gaps in
OL,15,Fchildcare provision for older
OL,16,Fchildren, including during school
OL,17,Fholidays, and investing in holiday
OL,18,Fchildcare and play opportunities
OL,19,Facross Wales."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
