OL,3,CParents in Wales face the highest
OL,4,Csummer childcare costs, research shows
OL,6,FThe holiday childcare survey 2026 is
OL,7,Fbased on surveys from local
OL,8,Fauthorities in England, Scotland and
OL,9,FWales, which were returned to Coram
OL,10,FFamily and Childcare between April and
OL,11,FJune 2026.
OL,13,FSome 199 local authorities returned
OL,14,Fdata.
OL,16,FThis report looked at the costs of
OL,17,Fchildcare and the availability of
OL,18,Fchildcare in Britain for children aged
OL,19,Ffour to 14-years-old.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
