OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784306880
OL,3,CParents in Wales face the highest
OL,4,Csummer childcare costs, research shows
OL,6,FThe report also found that a week of
OL,7,Fholiday childcare with a childminder
OL,8,Fcosts around #251 on average, marking
OL,9,Fan increase of 7%.
OL,11,FThe report looks at costs before the
OL,12,Fsupport available to help pay for
OL,13,Fchildcare is taken into account,
OL,14,Fallowing it to track changes in costs
OL,15,Fover time and recognising that
OL,16,Ffamilies can be eligible for different
OL,17,Flevels of support depending on their
OL,18,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
